---
import Layout from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Zoe Wacker"
  description="Student profile and achievements"
  pubDate={new Date('September 13 2025')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <p>
    Zoe is a middle school student with a growing interest in science, writing, and photography. This
    site is meant to document her projects, achievements, and reflections as she moves toward high school
    and, eventually, college.
  </p>

  <p>
    Her current interests include robotics, creative writing, and community service. She also enjoys
    exploring history and culture through travel and photography.
  </p>

  <p>
    Over time, this page will evolve into a comprehensive portfolio showcasing academic work, extracurricular
    activities, and personal projects.
  </p>
</Layout>
